WEBVTT

00:00.207 --> 00:01.855
<i>Previously on "Shades of Blue"...</i>

00:01.880 --> 00:04.526
<i>Responding to shots fired
at the Sunrise Cafe.</i>

00:05.464 --> 00:06.964
<i>I shot an innocent man.</i>

00:06.998 --> 00:08.699
You were on foot pursuit, he turned

00:08.733 --> 00:10.000
- and aimed his gun at you.
- Loman!

00:10.936 --> 00:12.403
Are you sure he chased a cop?

00:12.404 --> 00:14.204
A cop who ran away from a massacre.

00:14.239 --> 00:16.573
I'm not starting a war
with the secret police.

00:16.608 --> 00:18.242
You're not crazy. It's all connected.

00:18.276 --> 00:20.277
<i>If you really love me, save me.</i>

00:21.613 --> 00:23.747
Why would you do this to yourself?

00:23.782 --> 00:25.316
Somebody!

00:25.350 --> 00:26.617
She's an escort.

00:26.651 --> 00:28.218
Stahl calls her Harley.

00:28.253 --> 00:29.586
- Tell me what happened.
- I saw him.

00:29.621 --> 00:31.322
- Saw who?
- Stahl.

00:31.356 --> 00:32.790
Last contact was north
of the Mexican border.

00:32.824 --> 00:34.625
And that's where you think he is? Mexico?

00:34.659 --> 00:37.394
Is it possible you're using
Stahl as a distraction?

00:37.429 --> 00:39.430
Distraction from the fact
the intelligence unit

00:39.464 --> 00:41.165
<i>killed the only decent man
that I ever loved,</i>

00:41.199 --> 00:42.666
or that you helped cover their tracks?

00:42.701 --> 00:44.268
You know, Nate started asking questions

00:44.302 --> 00:46.270
about Nava's murder.
That thread could unravel

00:46.304 --> 00:48.105
Harlee's bad shoot at the Sunrise.

00:48.139 --> 00:51.342
Mr. Molina? Don't contact Nate Wozniak.

00:51.376 --> 00:54.845
<i>Why would I want to be
touched by some hipster fairy?</i>

00:54.879 --> 00:56.280
Let me go!

00:56.314 --> 00:58.916
You're dead.

00:58.950 --> 01:00.317
Did you ever really see Stahl?

01:00.352 --> 01:01.919
- I wouldn't lie to you.
- But you're not sure.

01:01.953 --> 01:03.153
Thought I was.

